Corporate spokesman Dan Fogelman claimed in an interview with the left-wing Huffington Post that a total of &quot;less than five&quot; Walmart employees left their jobs, and that the protest was just &quot;another PR stunt&quot; by the union that organized it.
&quot;Free checkout!&quot;
